title: #92Noon! Montage/Bercich/Boudreau/Grimm/Siny/Fleck
description: Vikings montage/talkers and calls out of the gate, followed by Pete Bercich in studio...Wild beat Montreal so HC Bruce Boudreau called in...Gophers heavy final hour with vox Mike Grimm and HC PJ Fleck making appearances, with Dave Sinykin sandwiched in the middle.
